Build directory to hold all the build tools

- env.Linux 
    Environment variables for building on Linux

- Makefile
    Master makefile for building all the native code.
    All module directory should point to this file

- targets
    List of user modules to be compiled.  This list is ordered
    in terms of module dependency.

- kernel_targets
    List of kernel drivers and modules to be compiled. 

- build_all 
    script to build all modules (based on targets) in
    release mode or debug mode

